Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:05.90,set,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(379,316)}江之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.52,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这片海上 有一条长着五个头的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.45,0:00:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶恶的龙的暴行让人们处于水深火热之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终 黑色的云笼罩了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深沉的黑暗降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都以为世界即将毁灭而要放弃希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一线光明刺破云层
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美得不食人间烟火般的仙女出现在紫色的云彩之上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙女的微微一笑 仿如在这个黑暗世界的点燃的一束光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(小田急片濑江之岛车站)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}于昭和4年(公元1929年)4月，在小田急江之岛线(相模大野站至片濑江之岛站之间)\N开通时建设的车站。平成11年(公元1999年)，被评选进入「关东车站百选」\N的片濑江之岛站，拥有使人联想起龙宫城的出奇驿舍，当初只是被临时设置建设，\N而现在已经成为江之岛旅游的标志性景点而获得人们钟爱。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 哥哥 乃准备咋办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(新江之岛水族馆)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我戳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 咋样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好的咩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真田同学要转学了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.01,0:02:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我想大家都会觉得伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过因为家人工作的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}转走 道别\N别离言辞 不失礼貌的道别方式 转学·转校·人事变动\N搬家是的道别信 人事变动·离职·结婚离婚·道别范文例文一览
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第几次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么最后 请请他向大家道别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 每次都不知道该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有留下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样看着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.88,0:03:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊… 又搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以搬那么重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 这是最后一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道别怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 是房东啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是谢谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会感到寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时日不多 但也多谢您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走了哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 接下来要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去很棒的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会发生好事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(很棒的事情)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:56.77,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(975,620)\fad(400,400)}忐忑不安地钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那边就是我工作的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}江之岛 Samuel·Cocking苑\N是明治时代的英国贸易商所建造的西洋结合的南国风植物园。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能看到海真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要现在去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天去也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是今天还是明天去都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多交点朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经是转校老手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑一个 挺胸抬头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 很棒的笑容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小沙丁鱼盖饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来有生的和水煮的两种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}东京天空树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,sky～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,tree
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(凯特 小雪)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.47,0:09:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小伊 这儿怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春啊 真是个好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(小春 凯特 小雪)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么能和我约好一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔皮欧卡（tapioca）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}tapioca是木薯，原产地有印尼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他是来这里干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 反正只是单纯的观光旅游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(腰越 腰越东高站)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不确定是不是老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许让座的话还更加失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 都到这份上了已经无法让座了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果不让的话会被认为很没人情味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是让吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是同一个学校的 她全部都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还为时不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定能够成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天虽然有两位转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一位好像迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能先做一下自我介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}真田雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个问好将决定一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以平常心来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音好怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我叫真田雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从大崎市来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转学次数已经不甚枚举
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过每次打招呼的问候总是做不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让大家觉得奇怪了我先道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 就这样子继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是什么来着 要淡定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的时候看到大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之岛有大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这种事情江之岛人都知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海无边无际 天空是湛蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气也非常新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为江之岛是一个非常棒的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要说所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没有想什么因为所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 总之先说点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 鼓掌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只要冷静地坐到座位上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要尽可能地帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚来可能有很多不明白的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要积极地帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全到座 应该说是至今以来最好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是站起来而已啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓竿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么拿这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.77,0:13:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才他说他是外星人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来过来过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来XN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没啊 我什么都没干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用那眼光看我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那个是什么鬼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一紧张脸就会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我控制不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这俩转校生都有些二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他俩不是正好配一对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去钓鱼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我差不多够了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么要去钓鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你的发型超帅的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.46,0:15:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去嘛 去钓鱼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(江之电腰越东高站)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个表情一点都不帅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？ 为什么 我又…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是早上那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海咲姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人和般若
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他们会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮球 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的兼职同学可是非常厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼王子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很微妙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子 钓鱼很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高中生里可是国家级的水准
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在学校里这么叫的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 那个水枪是个啥玩意儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会教我们的吧 钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙 搞什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 我可不是跟他一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错了 那是饵钓法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟饵钓是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}拟饵钓法LURE：路亚钓法即是仿生饵钓法,\N也叫做拟饵钓法，是模仿弱小生物引发大鱼攻击的一种方法,\N在整个钓鱼过程中,钓者是在做全身运动,与传统钓法有着极大的差异.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼这种东西 不就是老头子玩的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉没啥意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王子好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不钓的话就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪要钓的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要多嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在听别人说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说那个是饵钓法了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拟饵钓是要投向有鱼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那种事我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸什么毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鱼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺能干的么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好哇 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把钓竿竖起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我竖起来 该怎么提起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收线！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帅啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是洗鳃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:18:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}鲈鱼上钩后有个跑鱼绝招,叫洗鳃,鱼头穿出水面高频率的摆动,最易甩掉鱼钩.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲈鱼会用力甩身体甩掉鱼钩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一急你就输了 绝对会跑钩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑钩？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是会让鱼逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钓鱼很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天发生好多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我钓鱼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线断了 让它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也很厉害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人去的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 和班里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 说是朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.23,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 说到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我们变成朋友了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错哦 小春从今天开始就要在这里跟我们一起生活了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒的主意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 小春突然出现在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我连做梦也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救地球？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的会走到要拯救地球的那一步…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没想到
